channel.title: SRC (renamed client) not loading
channel.description:
Okay, I downloaded the SRC (?Silabs? renamed client), to aid in figuring out a method of loading a mapback. The only problem, is that it stops loading, no errors in the cmd, on 'requesting config'. I traced the error, and it is the 'unknown error' when abyte0 is returned as null. The error says 'connection error - retrying in X'. I'm fairly sure this is an error in the deob, obviously abyte0 is being returned as null, but I have yet to find the location of this. If you could help me, or know how to fix, please post. It would be appreciated.
Thanks
